::Hot Rod::

He tryed to jump back, but ten of the shots struck his chest, causing
some damage. He looked at his enemy. Dragonfly could not fly do to the
damaged wing, had a gimp leg, and had damage to the spark. It would not
take long. He once again fired two rockets at his opponent.
"Yield now, or die!"
